Class Request

java.lang.Object
  sasa.model.academic.Request
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClassroomRequest, MobileResourcesRequest
public abstract class Request
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract class REQUEST Class depicting every request a Professor can do. It contains some information from the request, and another interest topics. CONSIDERATIONS The huge constructor is the only one allowed in instance creation.

Author:
Gaston Charkiewicz
